channel.description:

1. Can you upload a new cache or something and convert a 508 to 525? Would you need to edit anything? 2. How do you add models to a 508 client or server? 3. If you get a new cache (like 525) and want to say use pickup to get dclaws how would u find an item list?
Any help, links, or suggestions would be greatly appreciated.
